The UTM is a complete framework that provides detailed assessments clients entire security infrastructures to identify, 
manage and eliminate any vulnerability and failure.

UTM is an advanced centralized solutions and configurations for distributed environments, 
well you can deploy sets of configurations instances.

Native LABS’s UTM is hosted on cloud, where Native LABS keep on your network, and could help your administrators and 
engineers to monitor your infrastructure and solve many issues.

Native LABS provide two kinds of clients agent appliance or light programs that you can host on your data center.
The Native LABS’s UTM core is an automatos developed with C and Python, that’s based on a modular architecture.

Features:
- Infrastructure design
- Equipment Specifications
- System Testing
- Risk and Vulnerability Assessment
- Security Systems Planning
- Audit and full reporting
- Patch and upgrade management
- Notification system (Mail, SMS, …)

Technologies :
Database : Postgresql, Sqlite
Language : Html5, XML, Yaml,  PHP, Python, C, Javascript, (AppEngine)

